<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="accustom-vt">accustom <strong><em>vt</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /ə'kʌstəm/    美 /ə'kʌstəm/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">固定搭配</h2>
<h3 id="accustom-oneself-sb-to-sth">accustom (oneself / sb) to sth</h3>
<p>1.<strong>使（某人）习惯于某事:</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>It takes time for the newcomers to accustom to the life here.
新人要适应这里的生活需要时间。</p></div></div>